<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (sydy ạlmsyḥ yạ mwlạy .. ạ̹nt wḥdk dạry bdạy)2
 wạ̹nt ạlly ʿạrf ạ̹nt ạlly ʿạrf .. ạ̹nt ạlly ʿạrf ʿạrf ạ̹dwạy
 1- (sydy ạlmsyḥ yạ mwlạy .. ʿmry ḍyʿth fy ạlkẖṭạyạ
 ạ̹nt kẖlạṣy ạ̹nt mnạyạ .. sydy ạlmsyḥ yạ mwlạy)2
 2- (sydy ạlmsyḥ yạ mwlạy .. ạ̹nt ạlbdạyẗ wạlnhạyẗ
 ạ̹nt wḥdk tbqy̱ mʿạyạ .. sydy ạlmsyḥ yạ mwlạy)2
 3- (sydy ạlmsyḥ yạ mwlạy .. ạ̹nt nwry ạlly fy smạy
 byk ḥyạty wbyk ạ̹sẖbạy .. sydy ạlmsyḥ yạ mwlạy)2</lyrics>
<title>sydy ạlmsyḥ yạ mwlạy</title>
</song>